{"tid":1166891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"封殺效應擴大 日本Panasonic有意中止與華為交易","createTime":"2019-05-22T17:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T08:46:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":291,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"a67965d1d8521959c91f40f4a3c633d6555b51c1","tid":1166891,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:10:53.000Z","msg":"美國封殺華為的效應似乎擴及到日本，日本時事通信22日午夜速報指出，電機大廠Panasonic有意中止與華為及旗下相關公司的交易。<br />\n<br />\n據日本產經新聞和日本經濟新聞報導，目前日本與華為有交易的企業已超過80家，2018年交易額度超過6800億圓（約合台幣1967億元），其中至少有11家大廠提供華為相機和電子零件等，除了Panasonic外，還有京瓷、村田製作所、東芝記憶體、SONY和三菱電機等，華為受到美國封殺也對日本企業造成影響。Panasonic可能為了自保開出第一槍，不過是否會引起其他日企跟進還有待觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2799145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2799145&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTSyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=e78ea5dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2799145&h=c521ec4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2799145</a>"},{"pid":"ee1a302017349098dbdf948edbacd97486e9e7f8","tid":1166891,"uid":32577,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T17:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"c25a9b5e6965e8225df825f768017a9dd1d102c9","tid":1166891,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdeb5bf352d174791f0d76ad918a80ddbfff8a4c","tid":1166891,"uid":76216,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T19:04:05.000Z","msg":"世界