 electronics maker Panasonic says it is ending its business with Huawei, following the US decision to ban sales of parts to the Chinese tech giant.<br />\n<br />\nPanasonic has been providing electronic parts and other items to Huawei. The company says its products, including software, that use parts and technology from US firms may be covered by the ban.<br />\n<br />\nThe Japanese company ordered its group firms to examine any involvements they may have with Huawei.<br />\n<br />\nPanasonic says it is complying with US regulations on export control.<br />\n<br />\nHuawei says more than 100 Japanese firms have contracts with it."},{"pid":"7178f32b06bea8ea71c1479cf34be8b043e85bd9","tid":1166891,"uid":33908,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T22:47:49.000Z","msg":"Panasonic好似大陸有廠㗎喎.咁激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dce63e5e2c973925472592ec93a1beee6efb912","tid":1166891,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T22:57:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63c371dcd4108d36a9e3755dffa2b2519e5ba4d3","tid":1166891,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:01:04.000Z","msg":"佢八國聯軍而四面威風"},{"pid":"ba7058c1f25fd5f6f1305de966731bcbbf408ef7","tid":1166891,"uid":42283,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T23:02:00.000Z","msg":"有生之年見到八國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1ff91def375797a5ca5d31bed49c10c2654085","tid":1166891,"uid":11148,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6319c7a01d9f5ccd8e3ea20dc6b33842a2e1e4f7","tid":1166891,"uid":173002,"like":73,"dislike":4,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T19:06:55.000Z","msg":"索尼唔賣sensor，Mate20同P30系都唔洗賣。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"r